data.description: 2 bedroom 3 bath, two story townhome located in the Club West neighborhood. Updated flooring on main level. Newer  paint throughout. Primary bedroom has a large walk in closet with a private bath. Large loft on upper level perfect for an office or another entertainment area. Newer countertops and appliances in kitchen as well as lighting fixtures.(Fridge will be replaced with different stainless one before closing) The HOA provides a gym, play ground, pool, tennis court and a party room.
